# ─── Whentor AI V5 — Environment Variables ─────────────────────────────────────
#
# The app WORKS WITHOUT ANY KEYS (smart scripted advisors + browser voice).
# Add these keys in Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables
# to unlock the full, production-grade experience. Then redeploy.

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 1. REAL AI CONVERSATIONS  (most important — makes advisors truly intelligent)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Each advisor becomes a real Claude-powered conversation with their unique
# personality. Without it, advisors use the built-in scripted engine.
# Get a key at: https://console.anthropic.com
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 2. CELEBRITY VOICES  (Fish Audio — real cloned voices)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Gives Elon, Trump, Goggins, etc. their real cloned voices.
# Per-advisor voice IDs live in src/lib/voice.ts → FISH_VOICES
# (run `node scripts/fill-fish-voices.mjs` with the key to auto-fill them).
# Get a key at: https://fish.audio → API keys
FISH_AUDIO_API_KEY=

# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# 3. PREMIUM VOICE FALLBACK  (optional — ElevenLabs, client-side)
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Used only if Fish Audio is not configured. Get a free key at elevenlabs.io
VITE_ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=
